{"type": "article", "id": 28799, "title": "陈冠希在巴黎发布时装秀，以及，Will Smith女儿接香奈儿广告｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-28T12:55:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 319, "name": "电商"}, {"id": 29498, "name": "光学实验室"}, {"id": 2443, "name": "杂志"}, {"id": 1164, "name": "数字"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 17, "name": "丹麦"}, {"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 2120, "name": "开云"}, {"id": 29499, "name": "Daily Paper"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 10632, "name": "UNDERCOVER"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 28551, "name": "Champion"}, {"id": 27283, "name": "Wood Wood"}, {"id": 14652, "name": "赫斯特"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 29500, "name": "Cosmopolitan"}, {"id": 6990, "name": "Warby Parker"}, {"id": 24698, "name": "Willow Smith"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703180041BuFl2sVUEoye30Mg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/06/karl-lagerfeld-miami-design-project\"><b>眼镜电商 Warby Parker 将成立光学实验室</b></a>｜眼镜电商 Warby Parker 继续扩张，增添更多实体店铺及 showroom。最近又宣布刚刚签订租约，在纽约创办公司首个光学实验室， 34000 平方英尺的面积。将为公司在供应链层面上带来可持续增长，同时创造更多本地的工作机会。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Uniqlo-to-open-first-Southeast-store-at-Disney-Springs-this-July,706111.html\"><b>优衣库在美国东南部开首家店</b></a>｜优衣库 7 月 15 日将于华特迪士尼度假区的迪士尼小镇开店，这是品牌在美国东南部的首家门店，两层的门店面积达 25000 平方英尺，将提供 Heattech 保暖衣、超轻羽绒, Supima 长绒棉制品、牛仔等等系列产品，以及迪士尼系列。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/cosmopolitan-amy-odell-named-director-of-editorial-strategy-of-redbook-10473470/\"><b><i>Cosmopolitan </i>杂志数字端总监将在 <i>Redbook </i>任职</b></a>｜美版<i> Cosmopolitan</i> 杂志数字端总监 Amy Odell 将加入 <i>Cosmopolitan</i>  姊妹杂志 <i>Redbook</i>，成为后者数字战略部门总监。Ashley Mateo 担任 <i>Redbook</i> 网站总监，向 Odell 报告，而 Odell 则将向赫斯特传统数字媒体高级副总裁 Kate Lewis 报告。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/intimates-activewear/puma-new-york-city-ballet-parntnership-10470146-10470146/\"><b>Puma 与纽约城市芭蕾舞团合作</b></a>｜Puma 宣布与纽约城市芭蕾舞团（New York City Ballet）合作，为后者全部 92 位成员提供排练服装，包括 leggings、暖身服装和运动鞋。舞者们同时将出现在 Puma 的印刷及数字渠道的广告上。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>Will Smith 15 岁的女儿 Willow Smith，3 月被老佛爷钦点成为 Chanel 品牌形象大使，近日为 Chanel 拍摄了第一部广告片，<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/27/12039628/willow-smith-chanel-eyewear-campaign\">2016 秋季眼镜系列</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180016CZQY45T8M7WhUO0i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62722646\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180016YrQMbEWwy61OXx2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180017LUgRIrwZm95W2hEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>丹麦品牌<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/6/champion-wood-wood-romantic\"> Wood Wood 发布了与 Champion 的联名</a>，名为 “RomantiC\" 系列，最后一个 C 字母使用了 Champion 的 C 形 logo。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180017LtnvhaIpbKP3iO41.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180018fbg6FioLCQ3h1K8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180019P0DlAvjUdLwgz7b2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">陈冠希创立的品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/clot-2017-spring-summer-collection\"> CLOT 在巴黎发布了首场时装秀</a>，背景是街道的涂鸦墙：<span style=\"text-align: center;\"> </span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180019Q3yhIvbKDpZJq2PG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180020ZJeWko5XARt7qaKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180021e8Q5xT2q7IHopA90.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180021MgqNOdw6mzLyHoaB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180022P9j1hITNvlJy7q04.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180023XWpHkZRqeSm8twrd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031800235EZ7Hn2QLIPUivCJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031800243BQjCkbhGi87a0lO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>阿姆斯特丹的街头品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/daily-paper-debut-eyewear-collection\"> Daily Paper 首次推出眼镜系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180025oeXspLIGhrzyCgnQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180025HmIkVhC3JdTupc8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180026OMWGJ6tz1rcRfTaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180026idLDqbYBj7xn8UsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180027eFkfniPNVJy8os7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180028KvEak1eCxdGRS7Mm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180028EORnp3Hd1xPDciZz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/lanvin-mens-spring-10472187/#!1/lanvin-show-runway-paris-mens-fashion-week-spring-summer-2017-france-26-jun-2016-52/\">Lanvin 2017 春夏系列男装</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180029wPDLrpdl3cfQkM7G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180029ZqncBuOFaWkXeH6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180031w7FaDjByYv6OzpWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180032q0YXUe2KyFrOS4NE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180032AVUJYTb8PrODyLQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180033g3lCkMjpHSTiYnUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>日本品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/undercover-spring-summer-2017-lookbook\">UNDERCOVER 2017 春夏系列</a> lookbook 发布，混杂了各个国家不同时期的元素，看起来还很舒适：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180033ZmypjuBYkwX9Krlq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180035iRujL8wO6qyfABYU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180035eNiYvzsDMLhUFJjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180036WMxIOg4eNEk8wAsn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180037pSWr0tQwR7IKP1XU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180038kWi3B01NIxQRFJZu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180038CIhiyAZLQFus2X9n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180039LkBChSrlMQt2Tj5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180040Cxt7Ps1A5mQYGqpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75449102\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}